    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238550/extras/32c1fe4f4e3f21554f2ce567306fc28b.avif?t=1732491680\" width=616 height=142 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Experience the thrill of grand strategy in a more manageable scale with Smaller Map. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >This <strong>Free DLC</strong> offers a streamlined experience with fewer provinces, but all the strategic depth and complexity of the original game. Explore a smaller map, conquer new territories, and forge alliances in a more focused and intimate setting. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Total Provinces: 5,532</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In comparison, the official Earth map for Age of History 3,  features a total of 13,892 provinces.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >When launching the game, choose EarthM to load the map.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3238550/extras/eb95a3fda6635c8a436188ad96b78c32.avif?t=1732491680\" width=616 height=288 /></span></p>",
